org.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM members INNER JOIN users ON users.id = members.user_id WHERE members.project_id = "$1" AND users.type = "$2" AND users.status = "$3"

rewrites.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM members INNER JOIN users ON users.id = members.user_id WHERE members.project_id = "$1" AND users.type = "$2" AND users.status = "$3" LIMIT 1
